            <div class="container col-md-8 safety-accordion" target="#sfty-acc1">
                <span class="safety-spoiler">▼</span> 
                Personal protection. 
            </div>
            <div class="container col-md-7 safety-panel" id="sfty-acc1">
                   <p>We made sure to always comply with the personal protective equipment (PPE) required for safe practices inside the laboratory. This includes proper clothing: long pants that cover the ankles, close-toed shoes, and long hair tied back. Apart from this a lab coat, nitrile gloves, and masks were compulsory.
 
                    </p>
                    <div class="row acc-images">
                        <img src="/img/portrait_placeolder.png" alt="img" class="safety-acc-img">
